title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Acid Lab Bonuses
content:
After last week’s smokescreen, the psychedelic scene is now firing with a full-scale production surge. Keep your Acid Lab stocked by running Acid Lab Resupply Missions for Mutt, earning Double Supplies to fuel nonstop output. Meanwhile, Acid Lab Production Speed is also Doubled, ensuring maximum profits.

Kickstart your career in the acid trade by investing in the MTL Brickade 6x6 (Service), complete with Acid Lab installation — now 30% off at Warstock Cache & Carry,
